'''Alliance Fleet Regiments''' were the main support troops for [[Alliance to Restore the Republic/Legends|Alliance]] capital ships, and were comprised of [[Rebel Marine|Alliance Marines]]. They would handle various tasks ranging from ship security to planetary assistance and guarding planetary bases. They wore gray uniforms and black vests and characteristic helmets. There were variations on the basic uniform though. They would typically carry side arms, such as the [[DH-17 blaster pistol/Legends|DH-17 blaster pistol]]. When [[Tantive IV/Legends|''Tantive IV'']] was captured by [[Anakin Skywalker/Legends|Vader's]] forces, most of the Alliance Fleet Regiment troops stationed aboard the ship were killed or captured defending it.

